---
import ToolLayout from '@/layouts/ToolLayout.astro'
import { LoremIpsumGenerator } from '@/components/tools/LoremIpsumGenerator'
import { getToolById } from '@/data/tools'

const tool = getToolById('lorem-ipsum-generator')!
---

<ToolLayout tool={tool}>
  <LoremIpsumGenerator client:load />

  <section slot="content" class="mt-8 prose prose-slate max-w-none">
    <h2>How to Use the Lorem Ipsum Generator</h2>
    <p>
      Set the <strong>Count</strong> field to the number of units you want to generate — between 1 and 50. Then choose a <strong>Type</strong>: Paragraphs generates full blocks of text, Sentences generates individual sentences, and Words generates a sequence of individual words. The text appears immediately in the output area.
    </p>
    <p>
      Click <strong>Shuffle</strong> to generate a different random arrangement of the same type and count. This is useful when you want variety in your placeholder text so repeated blocks do not all look identical in a design mockup. Use the <strong>Copy</strong> button to copy all the generated text to your clipboard with one click.
    </p>
    <p>
      The generated paragraphs each contain 4–7 sentences drawn from the classic Lorem Ipsum corpus. This produces realistic-looking blocks of text with natural paragraph length variation, which is more useful for layout testing than perfectly uniform blocks.
    </p>

    <h2>What Is Lorem Ipsum?</h2>
    <p>
      Lorem Ipsum is a standardized placeholder text used by designers, typographers, and developers when the actual content of a design is not yet available. It allows you to see how a layout looks with realistic text proportions without being distracted by the meaning of the words.
    </p>
    <p>
      The text has a surprisingly long history. It originates from a work by Cicero written in 45 BC called "de Finibus Bonorum et Malorum" (On the Ends of Good and Evil). The commonly used Lorem Ipsum passage beginning with "Lorem ipsum dolor sit amet" is a scrambled and altered excerpt from Section 1.10.32 of that work.
    </p>
    <p>
      The passage was popularized in the 1960s when Letraset, a company that made typesetting sheets, used it on their products. It entered the digital world when Aldus PageMaker began using it in their desktop publishing software. Since then it has become the de facto standard placeholder text for the design and publishing industries.
    </p>
    <p>
      The reason Lorem Ipsum works so well as placeholder text is that it has a realistic distribution of letters and word lengths. Unlike using "aaaa aaaa aaaa" or repeating the same phrase, Lorem Ipsum gives a visual impression very close to what real content will look like. This makes it far more useful for evaluating typography, line length, column widths, and whitespace in a design.
    </p>
    <p>
      When you are building wireframes, prototyping UI components, creating theme demos, or testing typography, Lorem Ipsum is the industry-standard choice for filling in placeholder content quickly and professionally.
    </p>

    <h2>Privacy</h2>
    <p>
      All Lorem Ipsum text is generated entirely in your browser from a built-in word list. No network requests are made and no data is sent anywhere.
    </p>
  </section>
</ToolLayout>
